byline.original: By SARAH LYALL and JACOB BERNSTEIN

abstract: Former Olympic champion Bruce Jenner is widely reported to be transitioning from male to female, which, if true, would make him one of the most high-profile people to go through gender reassignment; Jenner's transformation has been essentially on display given that he has long lived in public eye, most recently due to his extended Kardashian stepfamily.
lead_paragraph: Though Jenner, a 1976 Olympic gold medalist, has not confirmed it, he is widely reported to be in the midst of making a transition from male to female.

headline.main: The Transition of Bruce Jenner: A Shock to Some, Visible to All
